This lane closure will be nightly from 6:00PM - 5:00AM and is required to safely remove portable concrete barrier. This work is part of the&nbsp;continuing construction to&nbsp;replace the I-40 bridges over the Yadkin River and to widen and make improvements along I-40.&nbsp;As always this work is weather dependent and may be subject to change.
